  <data key="d0">ORGANIZATION</data>
  <data key="d1">. The entity that implemented the sustainability program, demonstrating a commitment to addressing environmental challenges.&lt;SEP&gt;The company has established a robust internal control system to safeguard assets and prevent financial misstatements.&lt;SEP&gt;The company is a business entity with financial obligations.&lt;SEP&gt;The company successfully completed an IPO in April 2017 and has since focused on growth, expansion plans, board independence, and governance practices.&lt;SEP&gt;The company successfully executed debt restructuring processes, resulting in financial improvements and growth opportunities.&lt;SEP&gt;The company that made the acquisition aims to improve its internal production processes and competitive edge.&lt;SEP&gt;The organization underwent senior management changes, with Michael Thompson assuming the role of CEO in November 2019.&lt;SEP&gt;The unnamed company made a decision in December 2019 to distribute dividends to its shareholders.</data>
